Perhaps in your limited experience.  And that's unfortunate.  Its also my unfortunate experience that most Wiccans I have met are drug addicts (in personal experience, I'd put the number at about 13/15).  However, I'm not about to make a judgement on their religion based on my limited experience.  That would be silly; and pretty close minded of me, dont you think?<br>
<br>
And since you've set yourself up to be the official person who points out hypocritical christians, do the Christians get to have an official too?  Its only fair, after all.  <br>
