For the ones who mentioned Hitler specifically, I found this interesting link:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.gospelcom.net/tmattingly/1999/col/col.02.17.99.html">www.gospelcom.net/tmattin...17.99.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
